data.description: Welcome to your luxurious retreat in the desirable Bayview beach area of Norfolk! This stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home boasts 2000 square feet of meticulously designed living space, featuring upscale finishes throughout. Enjoy the convenience of two walk-in closets, newer appliances, and a large fenced-in yard with an awning and shed for outdoor entertaining. With the beach just a short 10-minute walk away and close proximity to military bases and great restaurants, this home offers both luxury and convenience in one unbeatable package. Don't miss your chance to experience the best of coastal living in this impeccable Bayview beach home! Ask how to receive a professional cleaning and get your appraisal covered!
